STATE of New Jersey, Plaintiff-Respondent,
v.
L.F.S., Defendant-Petitioner. 079262
C-95 Sept. Term 2017 Supreme Court of New Jersey. September 27, 2017

ON PETITION FOR CERTIFICATION.

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-001805-14 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
